com.leantegra.wibeat.sdk.cloud

Interface ApplicationCmsClient


  • public interface ApplicationCmsClient
    API client provides interaction with Leantegra CMS API.

    For example: 
     ApplicationCmsClient client = CmsClientFactory.createApplicationCmsClient(context);
  ...
  client.getContents(new Callback<Contents>() {
      @Override
      public void onResponse(Call<Contents> call, Response<Contents> response) {
          if (!response.isSuccessful()) {
              APIError error = ErrorUtils.parseError(response);
          }else{
              Contents contents = response.body();
              //Use contents
              ...
          }
      }

      @Override
      public void onFailure(Call<Contents> call, Throwable throwable) {
          //Handle error
      }
  });
    Since:
    1.4.0
